Practice for OOP concepts:
1. DRY(don't repeat yourself): 不要在一个project里两个地方，一样的code
2. Single Responsibility: 一个class，一个功能。 超过30行要考虑一下。
3. Open Closed Design: closed for modification, but open for entension

DAO - Data Access Object  (Design Pattern)   不太懂 loose coupling, seperation concern

Java Logging : 好一点的 Syetsm.out.print

TEST:
each test should be independent

@BeforeClass
  @Before
  test1
  @After 
  
  ...
@AfterClass
